{"id": "1002290", "question": "线性回归的解析解是什么？", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p>平时都是习惯直接调包或者sgd的，突然被问到线性回归的解析解，一下子傻了</p><p>有知道线性回归解析解的吗？</p><p><br/></p></div>", "viewer": 6138, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "线性代数", "回归分析"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>线性模型</p><p>$$y=X\\beta + \\epsilon$$</p><p>$\\beta$最小二乘估计的解析解是</p><p>$$\\hat \\beta = (X^TX)^{-1}X^Ty$$</p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}, {"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>相关解答：<a href=\"http://sofasofa.io/forum_main_post.php?postid=1002489\" target=\"_blank\">最小二乘线性回归的公式推导</a></p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}, {"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p><a href=\"http://sofasofa.io/forum_main_post.php?postid=1002094\" target=\"_blank\">http://sofasofa.io/forum_main_post.php?postid=1002094</a><br/></p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}, {"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/robin_xu_shuai/article/details/75127386\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.csdn.net/robin_xu_shuai/article/details/75127386</a></p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}]}